  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.6.4\" data-text=\"Version 1.6.4\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.6.4</h3>\n<p>March 20, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.compose.foundation:foundation-*:1.6.4</code> is released. Version 1.6.4 contains <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/22b329dfa8888198eb3024650d236b3afe6c0907..1cbb6ee3e46f538bb2dc7ef6ce8e9c4b3cbc4dc3/compose/foundation\">these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>A long-press-then-drag selection gesture which moves out of the text’s layout bounds in the first frame of the drag no longer crashes. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Icdf907784adf27d418cd140864c1778dd73a9ec5\">Icdf90</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/325307463\">b/325307463</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
